            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Square Enix has released a 10-minute inside look at the creation of <em>Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</em>. <span id="more-1049849"></span></p><p>The video features producer Takeshi Ichikawa, director Masato Yagi, and scenario writer Sayaka Takagi, who discuss the creation process, the difficulties behind reimagining the original game, and what they hope fans will take away.</p><p><em><a title="Games > Dragon Quest VII Reimagined [18 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined">Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</a></em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2499860/DRAGON_QUEST_VII_Reimagined/" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/dragon-quest-vii-reimagined/9nkm0ckchdqx" target="_blank">Microsoft Store</a>.</p><p>Watch the video below.</p><h2><span>The Making of <em>Dragon Quest VII Reimagined</em></span></h2><p><iframe title="The Making of DRAGON QUEST VII Reimagined" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TlSiLOqewX4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
